About the Poster
This poster is created to celebrate International Women’s Day.

Summary
Women in Myanmar face many different hardships. 
Despite these challenges, they continue to do their best for their families, communities, and careers.

Detailed Description
This poster begins with my personal journey, showing how my interest in data and AI started through hope and encouragement, and how I have worked to improve myself. 
It then expands beyond my story to highlight the experiences of women in Myanmar through data. 
Although women face many challenges, the data shows that they continue striving for education, careers, and a better future, demonstrating resilience and determination.
